data.text: It's now been 8hrs since my #ModernaVaccine & the injection site arm pain has lessened after a hot shower/massaging my upper arm. I'm tired but nothing concerning. I had a bowl of ramen and I'm calling it a night on updates. You'll hear back from me on or after 2.3.21 ✌🏻
4hrs post #ModernaVaccine and still have the typical injection site arm discomfort/pain but I'm now very tired... 🥱😴 #StayHome #WearAMask #WashYourHands #ProtectHealthcareWorkers
